
    Code introduction : 
        scripts in this folder is used to train H2O force model from 
        CP2K dataset (from Yihao), Include core force and force of 
        wannier center. 

    ======================================================================
       Code name                       Discription
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------
      Split_data.py        Split Yihao's cp2k dataset to single config
       Ewald_sum.py        Calculate long range force in H2O system 
    ======================================================================
